node.title: Person dies in Waikato dirt bike incident
node.description: Emergency services are currently at the scene of an incident at a dirt bike park in Glen Murray, Waikato.
node.content:
["Emergency services are currently at the scene of an incident at a dirt bike park in Glen Murray, Waikato.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Diego Opatowski\n
", "At around 11.40am a person was reported to have come off a dirt bike and was critically injured.", "A Police spokesperson confirmed the person died at the scene and the Serious Crash Unit was in attendance."]
